</code></pre></div><h2 id='available-commands' class='group flex items-center whitespace-pre-wrap relative mt-14 mb-6 text-navy font-heading'><a class='absolute ml-[-1em] pr-[0.5em] after:hash opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-50 transition-all' href='#available-commands' aria-label='Anchor'></a>Available Commands</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/docs/flyctl/config-env/">env</a>    - Display an app&#39;s runtime environment variables
</li><li><a href="/docs/flyctl/config-save/">save</a>  - Save an app&#39;s config file
</li><li><a href="/docs/flyctl/config-show/">show</a>  - Show an app&#39;s configuration
</li><li><a href="/docs/flyctl/config-validate/">validate</a>  - Validate an app&#39;s config file
</li></ul>
